strings:
<voice_0x01001135><se_def>Cash: Look at you, Carrie.
This is what you get when you cheat!
You're pathetic!

<voice_0x01001136><se_def>Cash: I swear, you've been like this ever since we
were kids. Taking things too far and getting
us BOTH in trouble.

<voice_0x01001137><se_def>Cash: But I'm in a generous mood today.
All you have to do is beg me for help,
and I'll bail you out. Just like always.

<voice_0x0100113A><se_def>Cash: Carrie! Are you listening!?
Answer me!

<voice_0x0100113C><se_high>Carrie: Cash!? What are you doing here?
What's going on?
<voice_0x0100113F><se_high>Carrie: Whatever, Cash. You made your bed.

<voice_0x01001140><se_high>Carrie: This is what you get for being a cheater.
Now you're monster food!

<voice_0x01001141><se_high>Carrie: But if you cry for help like a little baby,
I might have my men give you a hand.
What do you say?
<voice_0x01001143><se_high>Carrie: Cash! Are you listening!? Quit playing around and answer me before it's too late!
<voice_0x01001145><se_def>Cash: Carrie!? What are you doing here?
